  "title": "DIGITAL MARKETING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Social media/Digital Marketing: create & monitor content for several platforms at once</li><li>Provide strategy on delivering content to the right audience on the right channels (Facebook/Instagram/Google/TikTok)</li><li>Follow brand guidelines to execute a wide variety of activities that involve branding, advertising, social media, partnerships and more</li><li>Create and design promotional material including posters, brochures, advertisements and other types of print and online media</li><li>Plan and develop integrated marketing strategies to increase lead generation and drive brand awareness, engagement and conversion. Frequently encompassing both digital and offline media</li><li>Brainstorm, plan strategies and execute innovative social media campaigns for multiple platforms according to brand guidelines</li><li>Coordinate and assist in any photography or videography needed in the execution of marketing campaigns and social media content</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree / Professional Qualification in Marketing, Business, Communication Design, Video or related discipline</li><li>Minimum of 1- 2 years of relevant experience working in relevant field</li><li>Creating and publishing creative content for multiple platforms should be second nature to you (Facebook, IG, YouTube, Tiktok, Google)</li><li>Experienced with Facebook Ads Manager or Google Ads</li><li>Basic design and image editing skills</li><li>Very meticulous, organized and digitally savvy.</li><li>Works well in both team and individual settings</li><li>Strong command of language, written and spoken</li><li>Proficiency in Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, Lightroom</li><li>Big pluses for Video editing knowledge / experience in Hubspot / SEO article writing</li></ul>",
